    "title": "Three Laws of Multivariable Feedback Systems, Extended Spectral Flatness (Extended Wiener Entropy), 'Uncertainty Principles' in Variance Minimization, and Performance Limitations in Minimum Variance Estimation/Filtering",
    "authors": [
        {
